| **Current Agriculture AI** | **Reality** |
|---|---|
| **Cloud-dependent** | 3.7 billion people have no reliable internet — agriculture AI is a luxury of the connected |
| **Energy-hungry** | 500,000 µJ per query — impossible for solar-powered field devices |
| **Stochastic outputs** | False positives = wasted resources, false negatives = crop loss |
